	    	</th>
	    </tr>
	</table>

	<table class="spacer">
        <tbody>
          	<tr>
            	<th height="20px" style="font-size:20px;line-height:20px;">&#xA0;</th>
          	</tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <table class="row">
	  	<tr>
	  		<th class="small-12 large-12 columns first last">
	    		<table>
	    			<tr>
	    				<th style="border-bottom:2px solid #008CBA;">
					      	<p>This purchase order was sent by <b>{{ app.security.getToken().getUser().getEmployee().getEmployeeFullName() }}</b> on <b>{{ "now"|date("jS F Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</b>.</p>
							<p>Please dispatch ASAP and <b>please book in on 01980 626880</b>.
							<p>Please send order confirmation to <a href="mailto:accounts@miles-apart.com">accounts@miles-apart.com</a>.</p>
							<p>Please notify of any price increases or any other issues, such as if you are unable to process orders by email or if a different address should be used, at this address: <a href="mailto:purchaseorders@miles-apart.com">purchaseorders@miles-apart.com</a>.</p> 
							<p>Many thanks.</p>
						</th>
						<th class="expander"></th>
					</tr>
				</table>
	    	</th>
	    </tr>
	</table>


